  "texts": [
    "Our Clues accurately represent event type information, and they are generated automatically.",
    "Unlike existing methods, Clues are type-specific and constructed without the need for human labor to design them based on different event types.",
    "The Context Selector in our method provides an effective context for event semantics in sentence-level event detection.",
    "Distinguishing from existing methods that recognize an event based only on a sentence, our method provides more event semantic information through context.",
    "Low-Resource Event DetectionMost of the existing methods relied on a large number of annotated data for events."
